  \bullet Solution: Remove password protection using PDF editor\par
  \bullet Alternative: Use unprotected copy of document\par
\bullet {\b Corrupted PDF file}\par
  \bullet Solution: Try opening PDF in Adobe Reader or browser\par
  \bullet If unreadable, obtain new copy of document\par
\bullet {\b Unsupported PDF version}\par
  \bullet Solution: Re-save PDF using newer PDF software\par
  \bullet Try "Print to PDF" to create compatible version\par
\bullet {\b Empty or invalid PDF}\par
  \bullet Solution: Verify file size > 0 bytes and proper .pdf extension\par
  \bullet Check file wasn't corrupted during download/transfer\par
\par
{\b "PDF page count incorrect"}\par
